properties.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued January 5 at 5:03PM AKST until January 6 at 3:00AM AKST by NWS Juneau AK
properties.description:
* WHAT...Snow expected. Around 2 inches of snow fell Sunday
afternoon. New snow accumulations of 3 to 5 inches expected.
Heaviest snowfall rates Sunday evening.

* WHERE...Yakutat.

* WHEN...From 4 PM this evening to 3 AM AKST Monday.

* IMPACTS...Plan on slippery road conditions. Travel will be
hazardous.
properties.instruction:
Slow down and use caution while traveling.

For the latest road conditions call 5 1 1 or visit
511.alaska.gov.

NWSheadline: WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 3 AM AKST MONDAY
